Imagine I walk into your house, chain up your children, rape your wife, and beat the living shit out of you.

Then, I take over your bedroom and say it's mine...

As the days go by, I decide that every other room is mine, too, including the washrooms and the kitchen.

Oh, but, I'm very gracious, so the broom cupboard is still yours and you're free to roam in there as much as you want, as long as you don't make too much noise.

I've also evicted your children and they are now living on the street in front of the house. Every once in a while they come knocking, but I tell them to fuck off and that "this is my house now."

Your wife works for me free of charge and if she doesn't obey I give her a good slapping here and there. I also talk about how HER husband is such a sexist.

Again, though, that broom cupboard is ALL yours. I'm a gracious host after all !

Now every single time you stick your head out of the cupboard and start throwing pebbles my way, I yell "TERRORISM ! TERRORISM !" and pretend that my life is in danger.

In "retaliation" for this terrible, terroristic behavior, I go to the street in front of MY house where your kids are living and I shoot one of them in the face and one of them in the foot, and then threaten you that if you throw any more pebbles my way that I'll shoot the other one in the face, too.

Oh and my buddy (who just happens to be the police chief), the one who told me that I could take this house "just 'cause"... He stops by every once in a while to say hello. I need emotional support at times, as it's so hard living in a house without a broom cupboard.
